data.description: Welcome to 180 Oak Street...in Leet Township! SO MUCH CHARM in this beautiful HOME. Offering 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath. High Ceiling throughout including large family/living room with beautiful cozy fireplace ....Spacious dining room with built in cabinet and updated kitchen with granite counters, stainless appliances, ceramic flooring for easy clean up and a spacious pantry closet for additional storage. Freshly painted neutral color pallet throughout home. Plenty of natural sunlight throughout with large windows, spacious master bedroom and updated lighting fixtures! Front porch offers peace and quiet with a gorgeous view...newly replaced decking. Meticulous basement for storage or future finish space. New washer/dryer included. ADT security system. New Roof. New fence. Added ring camera and light. Added keyless entry. New bathroom vanity with updated light (Edison bulbs).
